IAO_0022027 - wikidata q number

Label

wikidata q number

Definition

QID (or Q number) is the unique identifier of a data item on Wikidata, comprising the letter “Q” followed by one or more digits.

Definition source

https://www.wikidata.org/wiki/Q43649390
